metadata.name: Calypso
metadata.description:
The Panther is an extremely powerful and ancient totem. The panther, especially the black one, is a lunar animal.
The symbol of the panther means darkness, death and rebirth, it is a symbol of the connection of a person with astral entities. 
The panther also symbolizes the beauty and grace of movement.

Digital painting, oil.
 Year of creation 2022
